I"[<h1 id="changelog">CHANGELOG</h1>

<p>All notable changes to this project are documented in this file.</p>

<p class="highlight">Version 2.0.0 will be released on the 5th of December 2022.</p>

<h2 id="v200">v2.0.0</h2>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>* Major release. Introduced speedups and accuracy improvements. Version used for the preprint. (https://doi.org/10.1101/2022.11.28.518213)
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="v111">v1.1.1</h2>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>* Removed bug in haploid imputation
* Removed bug reading imputing regions with spanning indels (bug reported by @MySelvan)
* Removed bug in INFO score calculation
* Refactory model classes (cast)
* Added --inputGL option
* Added --ban-repeated-sample-names option
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="v110">v1.1.0</h2>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>* Better reporting of missing genotype likelihoods and ploidy
* Added multi-threaded input for VCF/BCF files
* Added haploid/diploid/mixed ploidy imputation
* Added FPLOIDY parameter in output
* Small improvements in the PBWT selection
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="v101">v1.0.1</h2>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>* Version used for the paper (https://doi.org/10.1038/s41588-020-00756-0)
* Change in the state  selection for phasing
* Bugfix for compatibility with bcftools 1.10.x regarding --main
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="v100">v1.0.0</h2>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>* First release. Version used for the preprint (https://doi.org/10.1101/2020.04.14.040329)
</code></pre></div></div>
